article.headline: Felton scores 26, East Carolina defeats Delaware State 79-50

article.linkText: Felton scores 26, East Carolina defeats Delaware State 79-50
article.story: GREENVILLE, N.C. -- — RJ Felton had 26 points in East Carolina's 79-50 win over Delaware State on Wednesday night. Felton also added eight rebounds for the Pirates (7-5). Brandon Johnson scored 13 points and added 15 rebounds and four steals. Ezra Ausar was 3 of 4 shooting and 4 of 4 from the free throw line to finish with 10 points. Wesley Oba finished with 15 points and nine rebounds for the Hornets (6-9). Brandon Stone added 11 points for Delaware State. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
